HSBC to Hold Investor Strategy Days, Sunday Telegraph Reports

-- B y   A l e x   M o r a l e s
-- 
2011-02-27T08:16:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-27/hsbc-to-hold-investor-strategy-days-sunday-telegraph-reports.html
  HSBC Holdings Plc  is set to hold
strategy days for the bank’s biggest shareholders, the Sunday
Telegraph reported, without saying where it got the information.  The annual events will be held separately from earnings
announcements for HSBC’s largest investors and banking analysts,
with Chief Executive Officer  Stuart Gulliver  set to organize the
first in May, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alex Morales in  London  at 
 amorales2@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Reed Landberg at   landberg@bloomberg.net . 